12:32.352 --> 12:35.353
Sounds like I'll be a fan
of your next album, too.

12:35.355 --> 12:36.888
Well, afraid I can't take
all the credit.

12:36.890 --> 12:38.389
You know, most of these songs
are co-writes.

12:38.391 --> 12:40.692
Yeah, well, sure,
but without the voice,

12:40.694 --> 12:42.193
They're just songs, right?

12:42.195 --> 12:44.896
Must be something special
about you.

