19:58.731 --> 20:00.364
Uh, ken devine
with wheelin' dealin'.

20:00.366 --> 20:02.066
I thought I was meeting
with luke.

20:02.068 --> 20:04.168
Uh, yeah, well, luke,
I'm afraid,

20:04.170 --> 20:06.904
Is currently tied up
with an urgent tour matter.

20:06.906 --> 20:08.139
He sends his apologies.

20:08.141 --> 20:09.807
Okay, I can wait.

20:09.809 --> 20:11.542
It might be a while.

20:11.544 --> 20:14.478
Um, I'll have someone
contact your reps for
rescheduling it.

20:14.480 --> 20:16.581
I-I'm sorry
for the inconvenience.

20:16.583 --> 20:19.417
It's all good.
Nice to meet you.
Likewise.

